Tests for libvirt bindings for python.

Outline of the structure of tests:

libvirt----tests----src----api----libvirt_python/
                                        |----LP_open.py (functions in libvirt.py)
                                        |----virConnect/ (Tests for class virConnect.)
                                        |----virDomain/ (Tests for class virDomain.)
                                        |----virDomainSnapshot/ (Tests for class virDomainSnapshot.)
                                        |----virInterface/ (Tests for class virInterface.)
                                        |----virNetwork/ (Tests for class virNetwork.)
                                        |----virNodeDevice
                                        |----virNWFilter
                                        |----virSecret
                                        |----virStoragePool
                                        |----virStorageVol
                                        |----virStream
